INSERT INTO `testimonials` VALUES (1,'Max is one of the more capable software development interns I had the pleasure to work with. He made a great contribution right from the moment he joined the team. He is \"The Improver\", always looking to make things better. Be it more efficient, more maintainable, or more performant. He likes to see things through and thrives on delivering the best possible solutions. Max will make a great addition to any team where quality matters.','Dawid Kucinski','Director, eCommerce Development at Tulip Retail',1,1,'2021-04-22 09:41:47','2021-04-24 02:46:41'),(2,'Max Mastalerz proved to be a fantastic person to work with. He is always punctual, his knowledge is vast and thorough. One of his best skills is his inquisitiveness in trying to fully understand problems in order to provide the most suitable solution. He also has an easiness to build interpersonal relations with others. He possesses a winning combination of solid tech skills and business sense.','Junaid Patel','Software Developer II at Tulip Retail',1,1,'2021-04-22 09:42:46','2021-04-24 02:54:08'),(3,'It was a pleasure working with Max on a number of complex internal initiatives on Access Excellence. Coming with no prior healthcare experience, Max quickly learned key concepts, took leadership on the assigned projects embracing a \"get things done\" mentality and delivering valuable results for the team. Throughout the 4 months he balanced the different tasks well due to strong prioritization and self-management skills. He was also not afraid to step outside of the assigned scope of work and support other teams leveraging his strengths in IT/digital and project management.','Artem Raskin','Global Marketing Manager, Roche',1,1,'2021-04-22 09:43:16','2021-04-24 02:53:23');
